{"tid":448313,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【外星人遺骸？】千年三指乾屍秘魯出土 專家：非人類遺骸","createTime":"2017-10-26T05:49:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-26T08:57:37.000Z","uid":79563,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"2b99f6692a27eb115c61692387d607c511564ede","tid":448313,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T05:49:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171026/large/1508955224_bc91.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171026%2Flarge%2F1508955224_bc91.jpg&h=225d3284&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n秘魯最近出土的多具乾屍，有科學家認為有可能是外星人遺骸。<br />\n<br />\n那五具乾屍在納斯卡（Nazca）的洞穴發現，有1,700年歷史，全部乾屍手腳各只有三手指和三腳趾。有人認為似爬行動物多過似人。骨骼專家維萬科（Edson Vivanco）認為，乾屍並非人類遺骸。<br />\n<br />\n有人質疑乾屍是人造的石膏像，但維萬科不以為然，認為只要仔細看，乾屍都是真的，目前未有證據顯示乾屍出土是一場騙局，又或者遺骸被人改動過。他說：「要造一個那樣精緻的頭顱，很費功夫。」維萬科保證，如果乾屍是假，他第一個指出。<br />\n<br />\n英國《太陽報》"},{"pid":"87e20e985ff9b529a0eb49d2bd3dab84b9e8db63","tid":448313,"uid":149566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T05:53:04.000Z","msg":"奪寶奇兵<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91b19d2350b0da97fd12d6641ec6d5192da22f03","tid":448313,"uid":152726,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T06:01:40.000Z","msg":"太陽報都有真野？"},{"pid":"3adf7e976415c23b295875bf3802074d7001ec08","tid":448313,"uid":70985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T06:59:22.000Z","msg":"駝背喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62ffa2f96de467e072305fb2aa4edc6d6da71503","tid":448313,"uid":12554,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T07:02:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple/20121027/large/27ec6p1n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20121027%2Flarg